trans-unit.source: Page within the TYPO3 system with further information or a profile of the company, e.g. “About us” area or a profile of the company
Detail page to the company profile
This logo is displayed in Google search results when the job is listed as a “job posting”.

URLs of pages on another website with additional information about your organization, if applicable. For example, a URL to your organization's profile page on a social media site, review platform, Wikipedia, ... . Multiple entries are possible here.
The name of the company must be given here (e.g. “Starbucks”) and not the specific location for which the job is advertised (e.g. “Starbucks at the main station”)
